The paper proposes a data structure for indexing large sets of keys, which is a fundamental problem in computer science. The applications provided are in the field of bioinformatics, which suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), or computational biology (cs.CE).
